reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My daughter ripped the rubber strip off our dust pan and I didn't want to purchase a new one. I found these and I'm glad I did. Here are my thoughts:- I thought there would be adhesive to attach this strip to the pan. It's not.- You essentially clip this to the end of the dust pan where the rubber strip would be.- It doesn't fit my pan exactly. It's a little long for mine.- The click fits snuggly and I'm not worried about it coming off.I deducted a star because of the assembly but other than that these work great.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Dustpan rubber strip replacement edge – 4 pcs
reviews.reviewText: Easy DIY for replacing the rubber edge on your dustpans. The particular dustpan that needed the replacement did not have the slip-on type of rubber edging. I manually tore off the rubber strip and then inserted the replacement over the edge. The replacement edge is quite sturdy and tight and appears to be of quality material. I expect it should last for quite a while.
